  "texts": [
    "As such, we welcome suggestions for improvement, and consider these definitions an explicit starting point for reflections, discussions, and empirical work on the foci of such disagreements.",
    "There are several methods to develop these DCT specifications.",
    "These methods differ in terms of, for example, point of departure (e.g., theory, expertise) and number of sources.",
    "We describe nine methods in Appendix 1, \"Methods to develop Decentralized Construct Taxonomy specifications\", and will describe five of them here.",
    "It is important to keep in mind that these methods are ways to elaborate construct definitions into compre-hensive definitions with corresponding instructionsthey are not ways to arrive at those constructs."
  ],
